criteria.driver_alignment:
DISCOVER — identified specific empirical claim to test (GME price error) and key event timeline;  
REPRESENT — constructed a table isolating dates and information types to structure tests;  
IMPLEMENT — retrieved GME and SPY data, specified AR/CAR market-adjusted methodology and plotting plan;  
VALIDATE — reports CAR plot validation and cross-checks with external sources (short interest, hedge-fund losses);  
REFLECT — links empirical findings back to EMH forms and broader implications.
